original_title: Tabitha and Kimberly's High School Reunion
overview: Tabitha Stevens and Kimberly Jade head home for their high school reunion. Kimberly fucks for a better car and Tabitha gets them some outfits so they can look like businesswomen. In the end though, their lives of partying and hardcore fucking turn out to be better than any of their classmates.
title: Tabitha and Kimberly's High School Reunion
